OL,3,CHeathrow blames dip in passenger
OL,4,Cnumbers on Middle East war
OL,6,FHeathrow airport reported its
OL,7,Fpassenger numbers fell by 5.3% last
OL,8,Fmonth because of the war in the Middle
OL,9,FEast.
OL,11,FThe airport said 6.7 million
OL,12,Fpassengers passed through its four
OL,13,Fterminals in April.
OL,15,FThat is compared with 7.1 million
OL,16,Fduring the same month last year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
