OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778526673
OL,3,CHeathrow blames dip in passenger
OL,4,Cnumbers on Middle East war
OL,6,FThe reduction reflects "the ongoing
OL,7,Fimpact of the Middle East conflict on
OL,8,Fsome markets and short-term
OL,9,Fadjustments to travel plans", the
OL,10,Fairport said.
OL,12,FHeathrow chief executive Thomas
OL,13,FWoldbye said: "We know passengers want
OL,14,Fcertainty when planning their hard-
OL,15,Fearned summer holidays, so we are
OL,16,Fsupporting Government and airlines as
OL,17,Fthey work through their plans to get
OL,18,Fpassengers on their journeys.
OL,26,@nD@XOUqD@\O]uD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
