FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778526673
OL,3,CHeathrow blames dip in passenger
OL,4,Cnumbers on Middle East war
OL,6,F"While we have seen some shortterm
OL,7,Fdisruption linked to the Middle East
OL,8,Fconflict, demand for travel remains
OL,9,Fstrong with current fuel supplies
OL,10,Fstable.
OL,12,F"April was still our busiest month so
OL,13,Ffar this year, underlining the
OL,14,Fstrength of a global hub airport that
OL,15,Fcan adapt quickly in times of
OL,16,Funcertainty."
OL,18,FHeathrow said it will update its 2026
OL,19,Fpassenger forecast in June "in light
OL,20,Fof the Middle East conflict".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@MO]{D@\OU|D@\O]
