PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778526673
OL,3,CHeathrow blames dip in passenger
OL,4,Cnumbers on Middle East war
OL,6,FThe airport insisted "underlying
OL,7,Fdemand remains resilient" as it noted
OL,8,Fits number of transfer passengers in
OL,9,FApril was 10% higher than the same
OL,10,Fmonth last year.
OL,12,FIt attributed this to an increase in
OL,13,Fpassengers flying into Heathrow and
OL,14,Fthen boarding flights to Asia and
OL,15,FOceania.
OL,17,FMiddle Eastern airports are a major
OL,18,Fhub for these journeys, but many
OL,19,Fpassengers are avoiding the region
OL,20,Fbecause of the conflict.
OL,26,@nD@VOUoD@YO]
